Tapaverse Guide

Welcome to the Tapaverse

MemeTapz is a digital universe of collectible meme caps inspired by '90s nostalgia, internet culture, and blockchain energy. Each cap is a character, a vibe, and potentially... a coin.

Meet the MemeTapz

  1. GRUMPZILLA

    • ‚ú® The angriest cap in the Tapaverse. Born from rage memes and pure blockchain frustration.

    • Coin: $GRUMP

    • Type: Rare

    • Skill: Rage Burst ‚Äì melts charts with one scream

  2. LOLBoy

    • üòÇ Laughs at everything. Even rug pulls. Built to degen.

    • Coin: $LOLB

    • Type: Common

    • Skill: Laugh Chain ‚Äì infects entire threads with chaos

  3. BRUHMASTER

    • üòë Feels every dip in his soul. Dead inside since the first rug.

    • Coin: $BRUH

    • Type: Uncommon

    • Skill: Sleep Mode ‚Äì disappears for days, returns with existential dread

  4. ZOOMY

    • ‚ú® Eyes wide open. Overclocked. Hyperactive degen energy.

    • Coin: $ZOOM

    • Type: Common

    • Skill: Speed Buff ‚Äì blitzes through meme trends before they trend

  5. THE THINKER

    • üß† Deep thoughts, deeper bags. The Tapaverse philosopher.

    • Coin: $THNK

    • Type: Rare

    • Skill: Mind Ping ‚Äì activates alpha thoughts across the chain

The Lore

No one knows exactly where the MemeTapz came from. Some say they were lost in a forgotten chain; others believe they were born from the quantum chaos of memes and memories. What we know for sure: they're back.

And they want to play.

The Coin System

Each MemeTap has its own potential coin. While they're not live (yet), the vision is to build:

  • Limited supply per character

  • Coin rarity linked to character type (Common, Uncommon, Rare)

  • Potential for point systems, rewards, or Tapaverse mini-games

Example:

  • $GRUMP = Rare, 1M max supply

  • $LOLB = Common, 10M+ supply

  • $THNK = Governance-style coin?

  • Follow us on X: @MemeTapz

  • Start here: [Pinned Thread Intro]

  • Join the future of digital caps. New characters dropping soon.

Tap in. Tap out. Meme on.
